{"tid":2423014,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連登陳同佳 #51346 惟有飲者L其M就快復活喇屌你老母：「貼ban圖唔洗ban，你吹得我漲咩？」","createTime":"2021-02-25T15:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T14:03:57.000Z","uid":343520,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9222cfd72e5067f6ad511e3fba8f9c1c44ca2d1a","tid":2423014,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"話說<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">會員 #51346 惟有飲者L其M</span></span></strong>，前幾日開左個咁嘅po：<br />\n<br />\n發明咗個可以喺office偷偷哋打飛機嘅工具<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2417082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2417082</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">（已被del）</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時Po中含有一張佢親自繪畫嘅gif，係一條好清晰嘅陰莖，比呢個所謂「打飛機工具」上下套弄緊，而<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">佢係冇遮冇掩下直接貼佢畫嘅呢張陰莖圖出嚟，但原來咁樣都係唔洗ban！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無奈事發後竟比<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">連仔秒速del po，破壞罪證</span></span></strong>，但天網恢恢，疏而不漏，竟然比我係google搵得返佢講過嘅嘢喎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">有人提佢貼呢啲圖係會ban ac，佢回應竟然係咁：</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv21aYA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv21aYA.png&h=d31b68ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">意思即係：</span></strong><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">係呀我突登貼ban圖，咁又點？最多咪禁言7日，你吹得我脹咩？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">咁嘅嘢都講得出，我屌你老母，呢個#51346 惟有飲者L其M同陳同佳有咩分別？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係管理員幾日前嘅回覆：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>管理團隊回覆：我們在收到對會員 惟有飲者L其M #51346 之舉報後，已即時將有關違規之主題刪除，並作禁言警告之懲處。請注意，會員在違反討論區使用條款後，管理團隊會因應嚴重程度、過往帳號記錄（包括但不限於曾經違規、被禁言警告或發現持有分身帳號等）<span class=\"orange\">以及是否故意或惡意等因素判斷懲處輕重</span>，並不會偏袒任何會員。<br />\n<br />\n回應時間：2021-02-22 00:32:02</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根據你哋嘅回覆，我想問問<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">公然挑戰版規，並表示處罰不足為懼，又算唔算係故意或惡意</span></span></strong><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">結果真係淨係禁言7日，人地都話明未驚過，你同包庇佢有咩分別？咁樣處理公平咩？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"744efef7ab5dbd1166df6dafdaaa28c7c8fde49b","tid":2423014,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce775662e04bb7e052f0e85189a0f642eba38860","tid":2423014,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"一零後會然點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4c065317efc9818f295f81d1533e34fd89b6a2","tid":2423014,"uid":231472,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"追擊個傻既<br />\n都唔知你傻啲定佢傻啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70eae43bb3f18e38a974f7c77b6bc1cfc78407e4","tid":2423014,"uid":343520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ce775662e04bb7e052f0e85189a0f642eba38860","tid":2423014,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"一零後會然點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"講真法官判啲串柒柒嘅犯都要重判以示懲戒啦，連仔竟然對佢藐視版規不為所動？係咪收左金錢呀？"},{"pid":"3cf4ad6faa803c6a2542628351cecd4b72ddd0e1","tid":2423014,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"抗議連囝del post<br />\n應該淨係刪圖"},{"pid":"ca8fa167402ebe8016d6a81a6989c6acdebb3f42","tid":2423014,"uid":343520,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e4c065317efc9818f295f81d1533e34fd89b6a2","tid":2423014,"uid":231472,"like":2,"dislike":1,"s